data.description: Check out this gem in the heart of Madison! Located in the desirable, Highwoods Subdivision, this split plan home is a must see! Located on a cul-de-sac with plenty of parking! Gorgeous back yard is perfect for those enjoying outdoor spaces! This home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths! The kitchen is equipped with double ovens and lots of counter space for those who love to cook or entertain! Contact your REALTOR for a private viewing and potential savings opportunities!
